Basic instruction to run client server appication

open 1 terminal
cd to wherever chatserver.class is placed, and type
java chatserver <portnumber(8000 and above)>
... server is up :O


oper 2nd terminal
cd to wherever chatclient.class is placed, and type
java chatclient <ip of server(in this case 127.0.0.1)> <portnumber(of the server)>
... client is connected :O

now connect another client guy from 3rd terminal and chat with yourself on both sides â€¦ lame ? :P